2026-05-12T05:52:04.8982606Z 12    <!--
2026-05-12T05:52:04.8982971Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-12T05:52:04.8983308Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
